title: Indonesia : number of internet users 2017 to 2023
summary: In general Number of users in millions has rose over the Year.
Number of users in millions is slightly increasing from 2019 to 2020.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2019 and 2020.
Maximum Number of users in millions, about 119.4 was reported at Year 2020
The lowest Number of users in millions, of value 107.2 was reported at Year 2019
